Ken Auletta , author of "Googled: The 
End of the World as We Know It," says "Republicans will cave" on
a government shutdown if the polls show a large negative 
reaction. Auletta talks with Bloomberg's Tom Keene, Scarlet Fu 
and Sara Eisen on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg Surveillance."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 02:51
 